OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776729782
OL,3,CWoman, 78, who died after dog attack
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FA 78-year-old woman who died after
OL,7,Fbeing attacked by two dogs in
OL,8,FWolverhampton has been named as Lila
OL,9,FHall.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to
OL,12,FWillis Pearson Avenue at around
OL,13,F11.30pm on Wednesday 15 April to
OL,14,Freports of a woman in her 70s was
OL,15,Fbeing attacked by two dogs.
OL,17,FDespite the efforts of emergency
OL,18,Fservices, Ms Hall sadly died at the
OL,19,Fscene.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/5
