OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776729782
OL,3,CWoman, 78, who died after dog attack
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,FThe two dogs, which did not belong to
OL,7,FMs Hall, have been assessed
OL,8,Findependently and are not believed to
OL,9,Fbe a banned breed.
OL,11,FA man who lives in the area and spoke
OL,12,Fto ITV Central said that for the past
OL,13,Ffew months another man had been
OL,14,Fregularly visiting the house with two
OL,15,Frottweiler-type dogs, which at times
OL,16,Fhe struggled to control.
OL,18,F"Everyone's friend"
OL,20,FThe family of Ms Hall said:
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/5
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,375,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F374A1776729782
OL,3,CWoman, 78, who died after dog attack
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"Lila, also known as Carol, was fun
OL,7,Floving, outgoing, hilarious and
OL,8,Feveryone's friend. We wish to thank
OL,9,Fthe emergency services involved and
OL,10,Fthank you for the kind messages,
OL,11,Fflowers and words from family and
OL,12,Ffriends."
OL,14,FA police spokesperson said: "We
OL,15,Funderstand how deeply distressing this
OL,16,Fincident is for the local community
OL,17,Fand we continue to have officers in
OL,18,Fthe area to offer reassurance.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@IO]
