OL,3,CWoman, 78, who died after dog attack
OL,4,Cnamed
OL,6,F"Our investigation is continuing and
OL,7,Fwe are appealing to anyone with
OL,8,Finformation who has not yet spoken to
OL,9,Fus to get in touch on 101 or via Live
OL,10,FChat on our website quoting log number
OL,11,F6073 of 15 April."
